movie.title: Anchors Up
movie.description_intro: After receiving an emergency call from Big Harbor during a fierce storm, Elias, a young rescue boat, pulls off a brave rescue mission and is hailed the hero of the hour. He is thrilled to be headhunted by the harbor and sets out to start his new life, leaving all his friends behind. However, life at Big Harbor is not all it's cracked up to be and Elias soon discovers that a local gang is mining an illegal precious metal that has the power to alter the weather. Elias realizes that what he most needs to expose the mining operation is the help of his old friends.

movies.title: My Little Pony: The Movie
movies.summary: After a dark force conquers Canterlot, the Mane 6 - Twilight Sparkle, Applejack, Rainbow Dash, Pinkie Pie, Fluttershy, and Rarity - embark on an unforgettable journey beyond Equestria where they meet new friends and exciting challenges on a quest to use the magic of friendship to save their homeland.

movies.title: Freedom Fighters: The Ray
movies.summary: Taking place on the alternate Earth, Earth-X, a world where the Nazis won World War II, Ray and his friends Black Condor, Red Tornado, and a handful of others fight against Nazi-aligned versions of popular Arrowverse Heroes including Green Arrow, Flash, and Supergirl, for the freedom of the world.

movies.title: Norm of the North: Keys to the Kingdom
movies.title_english: Norm of the North: Keys to the Kingdom
movies.title_long: Norm of the North: Keys to the Kingdom (2018)
movies.summary: Norm, the newly crowned polar bear king of the arctic, must save New York City and his home. But Norm goes from hero to villain when he's framed for a crime he didn't commit. He must work with his friends to clear his good name and help save his kingdom in a winner-take-all hockey match.
